commit.message: Instance of show added for generic basic_string.
Instaces of functor, monad and foldable classes added for basic_string.
type_traits split into traits and meta.
In Read type-class, read_any utility function added.
In monad, context-aware mreturn_ function added.
Overloaded consume functions renamed consume_char and consume_string (easy currying)

Utility function cat::forward added.

It differs from std::forward, in that it either return const l-value ref or r-value ref.
Utility functions words and lines added.
